&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;This is a full-time hourly position with first-year earnings ranging from $185,000 to $225,000.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;To learn more about earnings, promotions, benefits, and more – visit &lt;a href=&quot;https://gdba.com/join-our-team&quot;&gt;GDBA.com/careers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
